---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<Layout title="Insights" description="Thinking about AI strategy, creativity, and transformation.">

  <PageHero
    label="Insights"
    title='Thinking about AI, <span class="text-ms-green-400">out loud.</span>'
    subtitle="Opinions, frameworks, and lessons from the field. No '10 AI trends you need to know' listicles."
  />

  <section class="bg-ms-dark-800 border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <div class="space-y-8">

        <!-- Article Card -->
        <a href="/insights/execution-is-collapsing" class="group block bg-ms-dark-900 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-ms-green-500/30 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
            <time datetime="2026-03-07">March 7, 2026</time>
            <span>·</span>
            <span>5 min read</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-ms-green-400 transition">Execution Is Collapsing</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">What a 90-minute website rebuild reveals about AI and the future of work. When execution becomes cheap, the advantage shifts to organizations that can think, decide, and experiment faster.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Article Card -->
        <a href="/insights/the-earned-autonomy-gradient" class="group block bg-ms-dark-900 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-ms-green-500/30 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
            <time datetime="2026-02-04">February 4, 2026</time>
            <span>·</span>
            <span>5 min read</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-ms-green-400 transition">The Earned Autonomy Gradient: When Can You Trust AI to Act Alone?</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">A mechanism to know whether to trust your AI or not. Hint: it is not about capability benchmarks. It is about what the AI does when it does not know.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Article Card -->
        <a href="/insights/the-halo-organization" class="group block bg-ms-dark-900 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-ms-green-500/30 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
            <time datetime="2026-02-03">February 3, 2026</time>
            <span>·</span>
            <span>5 min read</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-ms-green-400 transition">The Halo Organization: Why Your AI Pilots Keep Failing</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">42% of companies abandoned most AI initiatives in 2025. The problem is not the technology. It is the pyramid structure you are bolting it onto.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Article Card -->
        <a href="/insights/the-future-is-ambient-ai" class="group block bg-ms-dark-900 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-ms-green-500/30 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
            <time datetime="2026-01-28">January 28, 2026</time>
            <span>·</span>
            <span>5 min read</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-ms-green-400 transition">The Future is Ambient AI</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">We have been thinking about AI wrong. It is not about making chatbots better. It is about a presence that knows you and is always there.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Article Card -->
        <a href="/insights/ideas-are-everything" class="group block bg-ms-dark-900 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-ms-green-500/30 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
            <time datetime="2026-01-21">January 21, 2026</time>
            <span>·</span>
            <span>5 min read</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-ms-green-400 transition">Ideas Are Everything</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">For decades, the startup mantra was: Ideas are nothing, execution is everything. That wisdom is inverting.</p>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA />

</Layout>
